General.Name: Dart Mining NL
General.Description: Dart Mining NL engages in the exploration of gold and base metal in Australia. The company primarily explores for lithium, silver, copper, molybdenum, zinc, tungsten, tin, and tantalum ores. Its flagship project is the Granite Flat located between Mitta Mitta and Glen Wills. The company was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Tallangatta, Australia.
